<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbfa1b5fe-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s12835"><num value="12835">§ 12835.</num><heading> Citizen participation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall ensure that each participating jurisdiction, and each jurisdiction seeking to become a participating jurisdiction, complies with the requirements of <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s12707">section 12707 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbfa1b5ff-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/625/tII/s285">Pub. L. 101–625, title II, § 285</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/4126">104 Stat. 4126</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
